request.description:
API endpoint for filtering cars.

Accepts various filter parameters via query parameters.

- `mark`: Filter by brand ID.
- `model`: Filter by car model ID.
- `generations`: Filter by car generation IDs (comma-separated).
- `yearFrom`: Filter by starting year.
- `yearTo`: Filter by ending year.
- `priceFrom`: Filter by minimum price.
- `priceTo`: Filter by maximum price.
- `region`: Filter by region ID.
- `milageFrom`: Filter by minimum mileage.
- `milageTo`: Filter by maximum mileage.
- `warranty`: Filter by warranty status (boolean).
- `orientDiagnostics`: Filter by diagnostics status (boolean).
- `fuelType`: Filter by fuel type IDs (comma-separated).
- `colors`: Filter by color IDs (comma-separated).
- `transmissions`: Filter by transmission IDs (comma-separated).
- `bodyTypes`: Filter by body type IDs (comma-separated).
- `isUsed`: Filter by car usage status (boolean).

Returns paginated results along with counts of cars under various conditions.
